 <span data-ttu-id="b7d88-107">경우는 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> 뜻합니다 일시 중지 된 후, 다시 시작 하는 표시 됩니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b7d88-107">When a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> action is triggered after it has been paused, it appears to resume and restart.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b7d88-108">그러나 실제로 오버플로가 발생 하지 않습니다,:는 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> 동작 실제로으로 대체 하는 일시 중지 해제 버전입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b7d88-108">That's not what actually happens, however: the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> action actually replaces itself with an unpaused version.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b7d88-109">될 때마다 한 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> 동작이 트리거됩니다, 스토리 보드에 대해 클록 개체가 만들어집니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b7d88-109">Each time a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> action is triggered, clock objects are created for its storyboard.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b7d88-110">애니메이션 효과 주는 속성에 이러한 clock 배포 됩니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b7d88-110">These clocks are distributed to the properties they animate.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b7d88-111">그럴 경우에는 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> 트리거되는 다시 해당 시계를 다시 시작 되지 않는, 새 시계와 대체 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b7d88-111">So, when a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> is triggered again, it doesn't restart its clocks, it replaces them with new clocks.</span></span>  
  
